{"lemma":"مِسْمَعٌ","slug":"مِسْمَعٌ","root":"س.م.ع","root_slug":"س-م-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/س-م-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مِسْمَعٌ","root":"سمع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n20739"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%90%D8%B3%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of سَمِعَ (samiʕa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n20739","headword_ar":"مِسْمَعٌ","root":"smE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An instrument of hearing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samoEN","text_ar":"سَمْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the latter half of the paragraph, in four places.       -A2-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A loop which is in the middle of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"large bucket called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garob","text_ar":"غَرْب"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and into which is put a rope in order that the bucket may be even;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) so called as being likened to an ear: (ElMufradát, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leathern water-bag called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mazaAdap","text_ar":"مَزَادَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is the place of the loop:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what goes beyond,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"through, the hole of the loop."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  Also, (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misomaEaAni","text_ar":"مِسْمَعَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (El-Ahmar, TA,) (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two pieces of wood that are put into the two loops of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"basket called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zinobiyl","text_ar":"زِنْبِيل"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when earth is taken forth with it from a well."},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Ahmar, K, TA.) ―         -b3-  And the latter, (i. e. the dual,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A pair of socks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stockings, worn by the sportsman when he is pursuing the gazelles during midday,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"during midday in summer when the heat is vehement."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}